Therabands are elastic bands used for resistance training to improve strength and flexibility. Secure a theraband under your foot or anchor it to a sturdy object. Perform exercises such as leg curls, shoulder rotations, or chest pulls. Maintain tension in the theraband throughout the movement. Aim for 10-12 reps for each exercise.

• Secure a theraband under your foot or anchor it to a sturdy object.
• Perform exercises such as leg curls, shoulder rotations, or chest pulls.
• Maintain tension in the theraband throughout the movement.
• Aim for 10-12 reps for each exercise.
